msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/date"
msgid "July 7th, 1943 · Ponyri, Kursk Oblast"
msgstr "7 de julio de 1943 - Ponyri, Kursk Oblast"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/mineprogress"
msgid "%1% out of 500 mines deployed!"
msgstr "%1% de 500 minas puestas"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/name"
msgid "The Citadel <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"
msgstr "La Operación Ciudadela <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/name_big"
msgid "The Citadel"
msgstr "La Operación Ciudadela"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Comrades, we have received intelligence that confirms the Fascist summer "
"offensive will commence at once! "
msgstr ""
"¡Camaradas, hemos recibido información que confirma que la ofensiva fascista "
"de verano comenzará de inmediato!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"We have dug the most comprehensive fortification lines ever to be seen in "
"history of warfare. We are ready to stop the Hitlerite hordes and drive them "
"straight to Berlin!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos cavado las líneas de fortificación más completas que se hayan visto en "
"la historia de las guerras. Estamos listos para detener a las hordas "
"hitlerianas y golpearlas directamente hasta Berlín."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"We've been ordered to lay as many mines as possible in preparation for the "
"fascist attack. Get to work, soldiers!"
msgstr ""
"Nos han ordenado colocar todas las minas posibles para detener el ataque "
"fascista. ¡A trabajar, Camaradas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/04"
msgid ""
"The Germans have commenced the attack! They already breached through the "
"outer lines of defence. Get ready to hold them back!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los alemanes han comenzado el ataque! Ya han atravesado las primeras líneas "
"de defensa. ¡Preparaos para detenerlos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/05"
msgid ""
"The German tanks are here! Watch out, we have been informed the Fascists "
"have brought new tank types, seemingly impervious to our shells!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los tanques alemanes ya están aquí! Cuidado, nos han informado de que los "
"fascistas han traído nuevos tipos de tanques, aparentemente nuestros "
"proyectiles simplemente rebotan contra su blindaje."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/06"
msgid "Well done Comrades!"
msgstr "¡Bien hecho, camaradas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/07"
msgid "The enemy is commencing a new wave!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo está comenzando una nueva ofensiva!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/08"
msgid "The Fascists are reeling in their artillery to help with the assault!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los fascistas están desplegando su artillería para ayudarles en el asalto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/09"
msgid "German aircraft incoming!"
msgstr "¡Avion alemán a la vista!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/10"
msgid ""
"We have received additional reinforcements, try to keep the Germans at bay!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos recibido refuerzos adicionales, ¡intentad mantener a los alemanes a "
"raya!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"We have received further additional reinforcements. It's time to drive the "
"Germans away from Ponyri and bring their offensive to a stalemate!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos recibido más refuerzos adicionales. Es hora de alejar a los alemanes "
"de Ponyri y detener su ofensiva hasta el punto muerto"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"Excellent work Comrades! Today will be a day to be remembered for many "
"centuries to come! The Fascist Beast is no more!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo camaradas! Hoy será un día que se recordará durante "
"muchos siglos ¡La bestia fascista ha sido detenida!"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Congratulations! You have stopped the enemy as ordered, a major achievement. "
"Your counterattack was a prelude to operation Kutuzov, the massive Soviet "
"counteroffensive which is about to end the German attack and crush German "
"hope for a big victory this year. From now on, the red army calls the shots "
"in this war."
msgstr ""
"¡Felicidades! Ha detenido al enemigo como se le ordenó, un gran logro. Su "
"contraataque fue el preludio de la operación Kutuzov, la masiva "
"contraofensiva soviética que está a punto de acabar con el ataque alemán y "
"aplastar la esperanza alemana de una gran victoria este año. A partir de "
"ahora, el ejército rojo manda en esta guerra."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"That is not the desired result! The Germans have broken through, and they "
"advance towards the town of Tim, somewhere east of Kursk. If the same thing "
"happens at the south pincer, we’re doomed, and the Germans will surely take "
"us prisoner. But maybe it’s not too late. Gather all the men you can find, "
"and go in again - never give up!"
msgstr ""
"¡No es el resultado deseado! Los alemanes se han abierto paso, y avanzan "
"hacia la ciudad de Tim, en algún lugar al este de Kursk. Si ocurre lo mismo "
"en la pinza sur, estamos condenados, y los alemanes seguramente nos harán "
"prisioneros. Pero tal vez no sea demasiado tarde. Reúne a todos los hombres "
"que puedas encontrar, e intenta de nuevo - ¡nunca te rindas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/place"
msgid "307th Rifle Division and 13th Army"
msgstr "307ª División de Fusileros y 13º Ejército"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/reinf_box"
msgid "Ammo supplies"
msgstr "Suministros de munición"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/reinf_il2"
msgid "IL-2 M1943 Airstrike"
msgstr "IL-2 M1943"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/reinf_squad"
msgid "Infantry squad"
msgstr "Escuadrón de infantería"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/story"
msgid "The pincer attack to encircle the Soviet troops around Kursk is in its third day. The northern pincer still hasn’t gained real momentum. This is caused by fierce Soviet opposition and well- prepared defenses.\n\nThe Germans push toward Ponyri and Olkhovatka. The area around Ponyri becomes the stage of one of the fiercest battles ever. The central front, under general Rokossovsky, is determined to stand its ground, come hell or high water.\n\nYou will be in charge of the defenses in this mission. Make sure you cleverly place some mines between the tank ditches to stop enemy armor from breaking through. If they do, fall back to the second line of defense. Make sure you hold the second line until our comrades of the 13th army are ready to join you for a counterattack.\n\nMake the motherland proud!"
msgstr ""
"El ataque en pinza para rodear a las tropas soviéticas\n"
"\n"
"En torno a Kursk está en su tercer día. La pinza del norte\n"
"\n"
"todavía no ha conseguido resultados. Esto es causado por\n"
"\n"
"la feroz tenacidad soviética y las defensas bien preparadas\n"
"\n"
"Los alemanes empujan hacia Ponyri y Olkhovatka\n"
"\n"
"La zona de Ponyri se convierte en el escenario de una de las\n"
"\n"
"batallas más feroces. El frente central, bajo el mando del\n"
"\n"
"general Rokossovsky, está listo para mantener sus,\n"
"\n"
"posiciones pase lo que pase.\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
" En esta misión estarás a cargo de las defensas\n"
"\n"
"Asegúrate de colocar hábilmente algunas minas entre los\n"
"\n"
"zanjas de los tanques para impedir que el blindaje enemigo las atraviese\n"
"\n"
"Si lo hacen, vuelve a la segunda línea de defensa\n"
"\n"
"Asegúrese de mantener la segunda línea hasta que nuestros compañeros de\n"
"\n"
"el 13º ejército estén listos para unirse a ustedes para un contraataque\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"¡Enorgullece a la patria!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/task1"
msgid "Lay down a vast minefield beyond the anti-tank ditches"
msgstr "Coloca un gran campo de minas en el exterior de las zanjas antitanques"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/task2"
msgid "Defend the dsmaged Ponyri station at all costs!"
msgstr "¡Defiende la estación de Ponyri a toda costa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/task3"
msgid "Drive the remaining Germans off Ponyri."
msgstr "Expulsa a los alemanes de Ponyri."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_07_ponyri/timer"
msgid "Defend the station at Ponyri:"
msgstr "Defiende la estación de Ponyri:"
